   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Benchmark Analysis — Schema Evolution on S3-Compatible Object Storage\n",
    "\n",
    "## Objective\n",
    "\n",
    "The objective of this project was to implement and benchmark a simple schema evolution workflow on S3-compatible object storage.\n",
    "\n",
    "The implementation combines:\n",
    "\n",
    "- Parquet datasets;\n",
    "- versioned data layouts;\n",
    "- MinIO object storage;\n",
    "- schema contracts;\n",
    "- backward-compatible reads.\n",
    "\n",
    "The project focuses on three reading modes:\n",
    "\n",
    "- `v1`\n",
    "- `v2`\n",
    "- `mixed`\n",
    "\n",
    "The `mixed` mode is the central part of the experiment because it combines multiple dataset versions into a unified schema before querying the data."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 17,
   "id": "82a52492",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
