   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "aca836b7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Correctness of mixed-version reads\n",
    "\n",
    "The first objective of the benchmark was verifying that the `mixed` mode correctly combines both dataset versions.\n",
    "\n",
    "This is important because:\n",
    "\n",
    "- `v1` does not contain the `device_type` column;\n",
    "- `v2` introduces `device_type`;\n",
    "- both versions still need to remain queryable together.\n",
    "\n",
    "The schema contract aligns both datasets before validation and querying."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 25,
   "id": "ff33c0e2",
   "metadata": {},
